content:
OmniScript Group Elements

ELEMENT NAME      ELEMENT DESCRIPTION 

Block              The Block element groups elements inside of a Step component into a manageable structure.

Edit Block         The Edit Block element groups together inputs to allow users to add, edit, and delete records.

Radio Group        The Radio Group element allows users to quickly answer a large volume of multiple choice questions in one step.

Step               The Step element divides the OmniScript into different sections.

Type Ahead Block   The Type Ahead Block displays as a text input field; the field auto completes results based on the user's input.

Action Block       Run multiple OmniScript Actions asynchronously by grouping them in an Action Block.
title: OmniScript Group Elements
